opencode-companion-codex
Copyright 2026 kim1232aa and contributors

This is the Codex CLI frontend of the OpenCode delegation engine developed in
kim1232aa/opencode-companion-cc. The Codex-specific parts — the MCP (stdio)
server, the tool surface, and the skills — are original to this project.

The shared engine code under plugins/opencode-companion/scripts/lib/ descends
from the following lineage (Apache License 2.0):

  - codex-plugin-cc (https://github.com/openai/codex-plugin-cc) by OpenAI
    — the original companion-plugin architecture and state-tracking pattern.

  - opencode-plugin-cc (https://github.com/tasict/opencode-plugin-cc) by tasict
    — the OpenCode adaptation of that architecture.

  - opencode-companion-cc (https://github.com/kim1232aa/opencode-companion-cc)
    — the hardened fork this repo's lib/ is taken from, including fixes
    harvested from the suharvest and JohnnyVicious forks (see that repo's
    NOTICE for the full modification history through v2.0.5).

Modifications made in this repository (per Apache License 2.0, Section 4(b)):
a newline-delimited JSON-RPC MCP server frontend replacing the Claude Code
slash-command/agent frontend; in-process delegation with MCP cancellation
mapped to OpenCode session aborts; task text carried in structured MCP params
instead of argv; a Codex-appropriate stable state directory
(~/.opencode-companion-codex); and host-neutral safety-header wording.

